    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-03-30T21:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-03-30T21:00:00-05:00" n="740"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d740">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">550.AD1/25: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Vincent</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Chungking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-03-31T09:00:00+07:00"
                            >March 31, 1943—9 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 1:40 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>475. Minister of Foreign Affairs<note n="16" xml:id="d740fn16">T. V.
                        Soong.</note> has informed me that Chinese Government has no objection to
                    the inclusion of the four named in Department’s 399, March 24, 10 p.m.</p>
                <p>Foreign Office has asked me to obtain from Department some indication of the size
                    of the delegation expected. I have stated that as many delegates as might be
                    reasonably expected effectively to serve would be welcome; that in view of
                    transportation difficulties it might be advisable to limit delegation to less
                    than 10 persons; but that I would try to obtain an opinion from Department on
                    the question.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Vincent</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
